0.4.0
* Added full support for banners. All banners including their details are now
  accessible through the Series::banners() and Season::banners() methods.
* Added Series::language()
* Added Series::hasSeason() and Season::hasEpisode()
* Added Series::isValid() and Episode::isValid()
* Changed buld system include dir: removed "tvdb" suffix.

0.3.0
* Added flags to the client. So far there is one: FetchFullDetails which will make the
  client fetch the full details of all series in a multi-result situation.
* Added writers and director to the Episode API.

0.2.1
* Fixed build error
* New make rules to automatically generate and upload the API documentation to sf.net
